Frequently Asked Questions
Quick answers to common questions about CADly

What file formats do you support?

We support PDF, PNG, JPEG, TIFF, BMP, DWG, and DXF files up to 50MB in size.

How accurate are the conversions?

Our AI achieves 90%+ accuracy on most engineering drawings, with confidence scores provided for each conversion.

How long does processing take?

Most conversions complete within 2-5 minutes, depending on drawing complexity and current queue.

Can I download the CAD files?

Yes! Completed conversions can be downloaded in multiple formats including DWG, DXF, and SVG.
